Parliament, Monday, 30 January 2023 – The Portfolio Committee on Higher Education, Science and Innovation will embark on an oversight visit to the universities and TVET Colleges in Limpopo to assess their state of readiness for the 2023 academic year. The committee also plans to engage these institutions on issues relating to governance, administration, safety and teaching and learning.
	
	Details of the visit
	Date: Tuesday, 31 January 2023 Time: 09h00 – 13h00 Time: 14h00 – 18h00
	
	Details of the visit
